<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1437,1861,2029]" pageId="13" pageNumber="518">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,275,1861,1885]" pageId="13" pageNumber="518">FIGURE 9.</emphasis>
Oscillograms and frequency spectrum of the courtship songs of two males (A, B) of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1767" box="[1144,1380,1861,1885]" class="Insecta" family="Baissogryllidae" genus="Gomphocerus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="518" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sibiricus">
